  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Beta-score</measure>
    <time_frame>6 months in average before second islet graft</time_frame>
    <description>Beta-score in continuous variable, using the last Beta-score known before the second islet graft. Beta-score is a composite score that reflects pancreatic islet graft function after transplantation and measured from the following criteria: severe hypoglycemia, HbA1c, stimulated C-peptide, fasting glucose, insulin dose or oral diabetes, glycemic variability.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
